<span class="header1">Arts/Communications paired with 
Protective/Military Service (BE)</span>

<p>If you show high scores in categories "B" and "E" you are a 
person who knows how to make things happen. You are very independent 
and have your own way of doing things. You like to use your 
creativity and explore new possibilities.  Teamwork and people are 
important to you. You are especially good at working on teams that 
are solving problems.</p>
<p>The occupations in this pairing often require some sort of 
specialized training after high school. Some require college level 
courses. Others require training programs provided by the company 
that hires you.</p>

<p><strong>Here are some career possibilities for you to 
explore.</strong></p>

